OL,3,CThe life-saving alternative to A&E for
OL,4,Cthose in a mental health crisis
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports correspondent Mel
OL,7,FBarham visited the centre providing a
OL,8,Fsafe space for those feeling trapped,
OL,9,Foverwhelmed and helpless.
OL,11,FA new centre offering hope to those
OL,12,Fwith mental health issues or even
OL,13,Fconsidering suicide is aiming to cut
OL,14,Fdown on A&E admissions for those in
OL,15,Fcrisis.
