OL,3,CThe life-saving alternative to A&E for
OL,4,Cthose in a mental health crisis
OL,6,FThe Crisis Harbour in Atherton,
OL,7,FGreater Manchester, opened shortly
OL,8,Fbefore Christmas as a drop in centre
OL,9,Ffor people who are struggling and in
OL,10,Fneed of a safe space to go to when
OL,11,Fthey are feeling trapped, overwhelmed
OL,12,For helpless.
OL,14,FIn just a short space of time, it has
OL,15,Falready helped save the lives of five
OL,16,Fpeople.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
