OL,3,CThe life-saving alternative to A&E for
OL,4,Cthose in a mental health crisis
OL,6,FSuicide is often called the silent
OL,7,Fkiller because people find it so
OL,8,Fdifficult to discuss, and it is the
OL,9,Fleading cause of death for both men
OL,10,Fand women.
OL,12,FBut for those people who are using
OL,13,FCrisis Harbour the centre can be a
OL,14,Fvital lifeline.
OL,16,FPaul Hindley was just 11 when he
OL,17,Fstarted taking drugs, and has spent 15
OL,18,Fyears living on the streets, a
OL,19,Flifestyle which has cost him his wife
OL,20,Fand his home.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
