OL,3,CThe life-saving alternative to A&E for
OL,4,Cthose in a mental health crisis
OL,6,FPaul says he is often been troubled by
OL,7,Fsuicidal thoughts, but before
OL,8,FChristmas he was at absolute rock-
OL,9,Fbottom and needed help: "I had
OL,10,Fsuicidal tendencies that week - strong
OL,11,Fones.
OL,13,F"So I came down here and it helped me,
OL,14,Fjust being here, its like a lifeline
OL,15,Ffor me."
OL,17,FOperated by trained volunteers it
OL,18,Foffers a more informal alternative to
OL,19,FA&E, and is open eight hours a day,
OL,20,Ffive days a week.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
