OL,3,CThe life-saving alternative to A&E for
OL,4,Cthose in a mental health crisis
OL,6,F"We just want an open door policy for
OL,7,Fanyone to come in and be able to get
OL,8,Fthat help immediately rather than
OL,9,Fhaving to wait," says staff member Rhi
OL,10,FPalma-Cass.
OL,12,FShe added: "Its not clinical at all,
OL,13,Fwe're all trained in suicide
OL,14,Fintervention, but we're just normal
OL,15,Fpeople and we're just here to help
OL,16,Fother people.
OL,18,F"I think everyone recognises that so
OL,19,Fthere's that level of comfort.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
