OL,3,CThe life-saving alternative to A&E for
OL,4,Cthose in a mental health crisis
OL,6,F"We genuinely care and we want to
OL,7,Fhelp."
OL,9,FWith emergency services more stretched
OL,10,Fand under pressure than ever, staff
OL,11,Ffeel that there has never been a
OL,12,Fgreater need for the service:
OL,14,F"Everybody knows our services are
OL,15,Fstruggling so much and I think its
OL,16,Fbecause of the high rate of mental
OL,17,Fhealth crisis," says Ellie Palma-Cass.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
