OL,3,CThe life-saving alternative to A&E for
OL,4,Cthose in a mental health crisis
OL,6,FShe adds, "So to know that we can
OL,7,Fsupport our local emergency services,
OL,8,Fthe more we collaborate the bigger the
OL,9,Fsafety net and the more support we're
OL,10,Fgoing to have for the public."
OL,12,FThe centre can refer people on to
OL,13,Fother bodies which can give additional
OL,14,Fsupport.
OL,16,FShould suicide prevention be taught in
OL,17,Fschools? We ask the question in our
OL,18,Fpodcast, From the North.
